text: Nisha Verwey (born 4 January 1984) is a Dutch-Surinamese korfball player. With her club TOP she became national champion. With the Netherlands national korfball team she became European Champion in 2010. Verwey has been a player of the Suriname national korfball team since 2017. She played with the team at the 2019 IKF World Korfball Championship in South Africa. ==Achievements== ===Club=== *Korfbal League champion, 2x (2011, 2014) *Korfball Europa Cup champion, 1x (2012) * champion, 1x (2011) ===National team=== *European champion, 1x (2010) ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Surinamese korfball players Category:Dutch korfball players
